<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.5.6">
<l>muriyum veṇṭirai mutukayan tīppaṭa muḻaṅkaḻa leriyampiṉ</l>
<l>varikoḷ veñcilai vaḷaivit tamaintaṉum vantila ṉeṉceykēṉ</l>
<l>eriyum veṅkatir tuyiṉṟatu pāviyē ṉiṇaineṭuṅ kaṇtuyilā</l>
<l>kariya nāḻikai yūḻiyil periyaṉa kaḻiyumā ṟaṟiyēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The man who made the vicious, cruel, striped bow bend with an arrow</l>
<l rend="indent">where roaring flames blazed,</l>
<l>To set fire to the ancient sea with curling, white waves,</l>
<l rend="indent">he does not come [here].	What do I do?</l>
<l>The glowing hot rays [of the sun] sleep; wretched me,</l>
<l rend="indent">my two, wide eyes do not sleep.</l>
<l>I do not understand the way the dark [night] hours pass</l>
<l rend="indent">[like] the long ones in an eon!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
